OL,3,CMy Community Series: The island Padel
OL,4,Cgroup growing by the hundreds
OL,6,FLess than two years ago, the Alderney
OL,7,FTennis Club was struggling to survive,
OL,8,Fbut now it is thriving.
OL,10,FThe man credited for the turn-around
OL,11,Fis Edward Hill.
OL,13,FEdward is no stranger to creating a
OL,14,Fbuzz around sports. He is a former
OL,15,Fplayer in the Spanish tennis leagues
OL,16,Fand also ran the Tour of Champions all
OL,17,Fover the Mediterranean.
OL,19,FNow, he's working his magic in
OL,20,FAlderney and pulling people together
OL,21,Fthrough Padel.
