OL,6,FHe says: "When we first started here
OL,7,Fabout a year and a half ago, the
OL,8,Ftennis club had eight members and now
OL,9,Fwe're at 240."
OL,11,FAnnie Burgess is a recent convert, who
OL,12,Fexplains: "It's got a lovely social
OL,13,Ffeel to it. I'd never been to the
OL,14,Ftennis club before, so I'm just
OL,15,Flearning padel and I'm loving it `
OL,16,Fit's really good fun!"
OL,18,FJoining Annie at one of Edward's
OL,19,Fcoaching sessions was the former
OL,20,FChairman of the Alderney Tennis Club,
OL,21,FJoan Jolly.
