OL,6,FJoan says: "It's made an immense
OL,7,Fdifference, we were in tricky times
OL,8,Fbefore this all happened.
OL,10,F"We didn't have many members and we
OL,11,Fcouldn't encourage people.
OL,13,F"Then all of a sudden someone came up
OL,14,Fto me and said 'what do you think
OL,15,Fabout having a padel court?' and I
OL,16,Fsaid absolutely and from then on this
OL,17,Fis what's happened."
