OL,3,CMy Community Series: The island Padel
OL,4,Cgroup growing by the hundreds
OL,6,FThe Club now boasts two courts funded
OL,7,Fjointly by several anonymous
OL,8,Fdonations, together with support from
OL,9,Fthe Alderney Sports Foundation.
OL,11,FIt's an initiative bringing Alderney's
OL,12,Fcommunity together more than anyone
OL,13,Fcould have anticipated.
OL,15,FCharlotte Newton has been playing for
OL,16,Fjust under a year and says it's
OL,17,Fbrought a lot of people together that
OL,18,Fwouldn't have otherwise met.
