OL,3,CMy Community Series: The island Padel
OL,4,Cgroup growing by the hundreds
OL,6,FCharlotte explains: "All age groups
OL,7,Ffrom 17 to 80 can play, and they are
OL,8,Fplaying. You meet a load of different
OL,9,Fpeople.
OL,11,F"I've made so many new friends and you
OL,12,Ffeel part of something which is just
OL,13,Fbrilliant. The Padel court is my happy
OL,14,Fplace."
OL,16,FThe club estimates that around 50% of
OL,17,Fthe island's active population have
OL,18,Fnow signed up - Sarah Simpkins said
OL,19,Fthat for many it's as much about the
OL,20,Fmingling as the matches.
